# Root Cause Analysis Logic

The Root Cause Engine evaluates:

```
Failure Events

      +

Timeline Position

      +

Frequency

      +

Evidence

      |

      v

Root Cause Candidate
```

---

# Example Analysis

Input:

```
10:00:01 eth0 link down

10:00:03 DHCP timeout

10:00:05 internet unavailable
```

Analysis:

```
Primary Cause:

ETHERNET_FAILURE


Confidence:

92%


Reason:

Ethernet failure occurred before downstream failures.
```

